                        <p class="Para">In this chapter we present our IoT Reference Architecture. This IoT Reference Architecture is, among others, designed as a reference for the generation of compliant IoT concrete architectures that are tailored to one’s specific needs. For other usages of the IoT Architectural Reference Model see <span class="ExternalRef"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-40403-0_3"><span class="RefSource">Chap.​ 3</span></a></span>.</p>
